* GLOBAL_O3  $ROOT/O3/v2014-09/MERGE.O3.geos5.72L.2x25.nc                 O3 1985/1-12/1/0 C xyz v/v   * - 1 1
* GLOBAL_OH  $ROOT/OH/v2014-09/v7-02-03.GMI/OH_3Dglobal.geos5.72L.2x25.nc OH 1985/1-12/1/0 C xyz kg/m3 * - 1 1

